sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as MLflow SDK / Browser
    participant Gateway as ODH Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant MLflow as MLflow Server<br/>5000/TCP HTTP
    participant AuthPlugin as K8s Auth Plugin<br/>(in-process)
    participant WsProvider as Workspace Provider<br/>(in-process)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant DB as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant LLM as LLM Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: Experiment Tracking Request

    Client->>Gateway: POST /mlflow/api/2.0/mlflow/runs/create<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (K8s SA)<br/>Header: X-MLFLOW-WORKSPACE
    Gateway->>MLflow: HTTP/5000 Forward<br/>Bearer Token forwarded
    MLflow->>AuthPlugin: before_request hook
    AuthPlugin->>K8sAPI: POST SelfSubjectAccessReview<br/>Auth: SA token<br/>TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>AuthPlugin: Allowed/Denied
    AuthPlugin->>WsProvider: Resolve workspace from header
    WsProvider->>K8sAPI: GET namespace / MLflowConfig<br/>TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>WsProvider: Namespace + config
    WsProvider-->>MLflow: Workspace context set
    MLflow->>DB: INSERT run record<br/>Auth: DB credentials
    DB-->>MLflow: Run ID
    MLflow-->>Gateway: 200 OK + Run metadata
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS Response

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: Artifact Upload

    Client->>Gateway: POST /mlflow/api/2.0/mlflow/runs/log-artifact<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Gateway->>MLflow: HTTP/5000 Forward
    MLflow->>AuthPlugin: Auth check
    AuthPlugin->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview
    K8sAPI-->>AuthPlugin: Allowed
    MLflow->>S3: PUT artifact<br/>Auth: AWS IAM credentials<br/>TLS 1.2+
    S3-->>MLflow: 200 OK
    MLflow->>DB: UPDATE artifact location
    MLflow-->>Gateway: 200 OK
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS Response

    Note over Client,LLM: Flow 3: AI Gateway LLM Invocation

    Client->>Gateway: POST /mlflow/gateway/openai/v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Gateway->>MLflow: HTTP/5000 Forward
    MLflow->>AuthPlugin: Auth check
    AuthPlugin->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview
    K8sAPI-->>AuthPlugin: Allowed
    MLflow->>DB: SELECT provider config<br/>Decrypt API key (AES-256-GCM KEK)
    DB-->>MLflow: Encrypted provider config
    MLflow->>LLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: API key (KEK-decrypted)<br/>TLS 1.2+
    LLM-->>MLflow: Chat completion response
    MLflow-->>Gateway: 200 OK + LLM response
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS Response

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 4: OTLP Trace Ingestion

    Client->>MLflow: POST /v1/traces<br/>Auth: Bearer Token<br/>Header: x-mlflow-experiment-id<br/>Content-Type: application/x-protobuf
    MLflow->>AuthPlugin: Auth check (experiment-scoped)
    AuthPlugin->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview
    K8sAPI-->>AuthPlugin: Allowed
    MLflow->>DB: INSERT trace spans
    MLflow->>S3: PUT trace artifacts<br/>TLS 1.2+
    MLflow-->>Client: 200 OK
